Dùng google translate 
Theo link : https://github.com/statickidz/php-google-translate-free 
Youtube: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gfdak8YHjiU&ab_channel=Computerjulian

1.	CÀi 
$ composer require statickidz/php-google-translate-free 

2.	Chép đoạn code ví dụ
require_once ('vendor/autoload.php');
use \Statickidz\GoogleTranslate;

$source = 'es';
$target = 'en';
$text = 'buenos días';

$trans = new GoogleTranslate();
$result = $trans->translate($source, $target, $text);

// Good morning
echo $result;

3.	Run
Link mở rộng hơn cài    $ composer require google/cloud-translate
https://github.com/googleapis/google-cloud-php-translate?fbclid=IwAR0FadcHS2dq9WVR_T8O0XJmenD3C85XGzIWgyxXK07qfYXnZUEOkVYJkkY

